Zero point energy                ...      0.67922804 Eh     426.22 kcal/mol
Thermal vibrational correction   ...      0.04031676 Eh      25.30 kcal/mol
Thermal rotational correction    ...      0.00141627 Eh       0.89 kcal/mol
